Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.35,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}对着无法起飞的螺旋桨做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:25.81,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝着天空的另一半抬头望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.92,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光着脚丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:33.36,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我们永远都是
